The paper focuses on the use of drones for warehouse management tasks, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) category. The paper also extensively uses image processing techniques for line detection and localization, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The paper also discusses the use of Kalman filter for smoothening the outputs, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) category. Finally, the paper discusses the navigation of the drone in a structured environment, which falls under systems and control (cs.SY) category.
